Imagine that you are doing a project on what presents people like giving most in Zetland. You have found some data on the subject - the results of the opinion polls (see the diagram below).
Comment on the data in the diagram and give your opinion on the subject of the project.

What presents people like giving most

Write 200-250 words.
Use the following plan:
- make an opening statement on the subject of the project;
- select and report 2-3 facts;
- make 1-2 comparisons where relevant;
- outline a problem that can arise with giving presents and suggest a way of solving it;
- conclude by giving your opinion on the role of giving and receiving presents in life.
